children.leading_comment:
*
@desc Update the global wheelchair parameters using the provided type and newParams.
This function merges newParams with the current (or manual) parameters
and, if the type is "powered", updates additional powered-specific parameters.
@param {string} type - The wheelchair type ("manual" or "powered").
@param {Object} newParams - An object containing new parameter values to update.

